    <entry>
      <title>git命令</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/05/git%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/05/git%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-git初始化基本操作"><a href="#1-git初始化基本操作" class="headerlink" title="1.git初始化基本操作"></a>1.git初始化基本操作</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">账号</span><br><span class="line">邮箱</span><br><span class="line">生成key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-1git初始化提交代码"><a href="#1-1git初始化提交代码" class="headerlink" title="1.1git初始化提交代码"></a>1.1git初始化提交代码</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. git add . </span><br><span class="line">2. git commit -m &quot;提交信息&quot;</span><br><span class="line">3. git push -u origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2git切换远程仓库"><a href="#1-2git切换远程仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.2git切换远程仓库"></a>1.2git切换远程仓库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 直接修改远程仓库</span><br><span class="line">    git remote set-url origin 新的远程仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">2. 先删除后添加</span><br><span class="line">    a. 删除 git remote rm origin</span><br><span class="line">    b. 添加 git remote add origin 新的远程仓库地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-3git基本命令"><a href="#1-3git基本命令" class="headerlink" title="1.3git基本命令"></a>1.3git基本命令</h2><table><thead><tr><th>序号</th><th>功能</th><th>命令</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>拉取远程代码</td><td>git git pull</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>查看本地分支</td><td>git branch</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>查看远程分支</td><td>git branch -r</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>查看所有分支</td><td>git branch -a</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>创建本地分支</td><td>git branch  branchName</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>建立本地分支与远程分支的联系</td><td>git branch –set-upstream-to=origin/&lt; branch &gt; feture-test</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>重命名分支</td><td>git branch -m old new / git branch -M old new</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>删除本地分支</td><td>git branch -a</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>删除远程分支</td><td>git branch -d -r branchname</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>查看在你上次提交之后是否有对文件进行再次修改</td><td>git status</td></tr><tr><td>11</td><td>删除远程分支</td><td>git add .</td></tr><tr><td>12</td><td>删除远程分支</td><td>git commit -m</td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>将远程仓库origin的master分支与本地仓库master分支关联</td><td>git push -u origin master</td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>提交代码</td><td>git push</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="2-git配置忽略文件"><a href="#2-git配置忽略文件" class="headerlink" title="2.git配置忽略文件"></a>2.git配置忽略文件</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. Git Bash进入命令行，输入touch .gitignore，生成.gitignore文件。</span><br><span class="line">2. 添加以下内容</span><br><span class="line">    // .gitignore文件</span><br><span class="line">    node_modules/</span><br><span class="line">    dist/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>以斜杠“/”开头表示目录；<br>以星号“*”通配多个字符；<br>以问号“?”通配单个字符；<br>以方括号“[]”包含单个字符的匹配列表；<br>以叹号“!”表示不忽略(跟踪)匹配到的文件或目录</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> git </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
